channel.title: The server -------------- offline, it must be online before you can register it
channel.description:
I got this error message when I went to post my status on the status checker page.
It says it's offline when Its online, Im on it now on my own, but im on it via my no-ip address (drpkay.no-ip.biz)
PLEASE HELP ME HERE, THANKS!

item.description:

Need for speed111:

did you portforward correctly? and make sure no-ip is checked all i can think of

Yes portforwarded correctly. But my no-ip host ip thing is my ip like “81…” so on. Shoudld it be set to the ip that i portforwarded with?

The ip that you get from doing “CMD” “ipconfig”???

Thanks
